On the Romanian analyzer, using a **wildcard** for a stop word in a **simple_query_string** generates a **MatchNoDocsQuery**, which prevents matching any documents. The expected behavior is to remove the stop word from the query instead of generating a `MatchNoDocsQuery`. This behavior seems similar to issue [#1272](https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/issues/1272).

